name: Retouching and Photo Restoration
description: available for any picture regardless of weather or not i was the photographer who shot it. i can zap out acne, remove redeye, correct color balance or even change the color of your hair or outfit with my retouching service.  got an old family photo that hasn't withstood the test of time very well? or maybe your favorite photo was the victim of an unfortunate accident that caused  severe  damage. do not fear, for i can bring it back to life making it look as good as new, even better most of the time!  Retouche = $20 per image  Restoration = $50 per hour

name: private photography instruction
description: do you want to learn how to take better pictures? weather you aspire to become a profesional photographer or just want to grasp a better understanding of your hobby, i can teach you everything from the basic fundamentals to advanced techniques. all in depth, i'll make sure you receive as much valuable knowledge as possible.  $150 for a personalized  lesson that can last up to 3 hours without additional charges. each lesson includes 1 part lecture and 1 shooting session so you can practice what your learning with me there to ensure your development is on track. and finally, each lesson includes one homework assignment that you can submit electronically and i will provide you with critical analysis feedback.

name: Portrait or Product photoShoot
description:
i would be happy to shoot professional portraits for you, your band, your family, or even your pet. your choice of studio or outdoor @ any location. 
same rates apply if you want to hire me to shoot your product line.  
$100.00 per hour. time starts when the first frame is shot. 
photos furnished digitally via online gallery@ ryanraynerphotography.com
prints extra. available from website when you download your photos.
retouching= 1 free retouch per shoot on the image of your choice. extra retouching services available from THIS site. see 'Retouching'
from the main menu.

name: Event Photography
description: you can hire me to shoot your event, weather it be a wedding, concert, or a child's birthday party. no event is too big or too small. contact me at RyanRayner13@gmail.com to discuss pricing and book me for your event today!

name: Donation
description:
do you enjoy my work? i work on average 16 hours a day, 7 days a week, and essentialy for free...i put myself through such an intense grind day in and day out hoping that eventually the steady flow of new content helps me land a good job, or a sponsorship, gallery exhibition or even just generates a few print sales now and then...somethings gotta give eventually, right? but until that day comes, im gonna be right here, panhandling on the interwebz... sooo...excuse me sir/miss? got any spare change? 

help support your favorite starving artist by making a donation, anything is better than nothing at all. thank you kindly.
